reviews.review_text:
Divine Providence!  Great stuff and a very fine recording from Mr. Hill; not sure why no comments...Alas, Yet another super fine night in Providence, staple New England venue for years. Great playing both nights this run; Hitchhiked to this night. Friday had an old timey looseness, great Althea, BRR/Music, Playin', China Doll/High Time! (first since Fall 82). whole show great, Row, Wharfrat-Big JG showing, esp. set 2.
32 years ago today! Was 18 yrs and The Clash was touring East Coast simultaneously. Where does the time go??!!
